Checklist Comments: observers=Haven Wiley; others=Minna Wiley; vehicles=15; habitat@1R=BB (formerly P); weather=70-75F, overcast becoming clear, no wind; notes=BHVI in pines with reduced understory as usual; no CWWI nor EWPW at stop 1R (both formerly regular here before habitat changed to B this year); CWWI heard at stop 3L (where occasionally heard formerly); EWPW heard 1.0 miles north of stop 1 (see pre-count on this date); BHVI singing in pine flatwoods (tall pines managed to reduce understory) in same habitat and same general location where it has occurred on these censuses for the past 20 years!
